<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="faint-adj">faint <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /feɪnt/    美 /feɪnt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>眩晕的；虚弱的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was <strong>faint with</strong> hunger.
我饿得头晕眼花。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-slight">2.★ <strong>(光、声、味等) 微弱的；微小的 (slight)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>the faint</strong> memory / <strong>light</strong>
模糊的记忆/微弱的光</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a faint hope</strong> / <strong>chance</strong>
很小的希望/机会</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>faintly /'feɪntli/ adv   </p></div>